&lt;p>If you aren&amp;rsquo;t familiar with the &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Einstellung_effect">Einstellung Effect&lt;/a> or &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Law_of_the_instrument">The Law of the Instrument&lt;/a>, they essentially claim that we only try to solve a problem based on what we already know (past experience).
&lt;img src="images/js_meme.png" alt="img.png">
